headline: Humana Foundation Report Exposes Epidemic of Loneliness Among Underserved Boys
summary: LOUISVILLE, Ky., December 17, 2025--The Humana Foundation, the philanthropic arm of Humana Inc. for the past 44 years, today announced the publication of its new report, "Strengthening Belonging for Underserved Boys." headline: Humana taps ex-Amazon executive as incoming insurance head
summary: George Renaudin, who has been with Humana for almost 30 years, is retiring, the insurer announced Tuesday. Aaron Martin, previously Amazon’s vice president of healthcare, will take his place.
